"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-07-31-gymnasts-use-chalk-olympics-21334017\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"If you are watching gymnastics at theOlympics, you can not help but notice that every competitor is using chalk.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 20, \"to\": 30}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympics\", \"from\": 34, \"to\": 45}, {\"ngram\": \"every competitor\", \"from\": 80, \"to\": 96}, {\"ngram\": \"chalk\", \"from\": 106, \"to\": 111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For all gymnasts competing on bars, rings, pommel horse and even the balance beam, chalk is an essential part of the preparation moments before a routine.\", \"from\": 114, \"to\": 268, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all gymnasts\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 130}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 144, \"to\": 148}, {\"ngram\": \"rings\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 155}, {\"ngram\": \"pommel horse\", \"from\": 157, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"even the balance beam\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 195}, {\"ngram\": \"chalk\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 202}, {\"ngram\": \"an essential part\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 223}, {\"ngram\": \"the preparation\", \"from\": 227, \"to\": 242}, {\"ngram\": \"a routine\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chalk is undoubtedly messy to use, some commercial gyms have even banned it due to the extensive clean up required.\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 385, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chalk\", \"from\": 270, \"to\": 275}, {\"ngram\": \"some commercial gyms\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"the extensive clean\", \"from\": 353, \"to\": 372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for elite gymnasts, chalk will remain a vital tool in the sport.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"elite gymnasts\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 409}, {\"ngram\": \"chalk\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"a vital tool\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chalk is vital for gymnasts to ensure that they can maintain their strong grip.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 536, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Chalk\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 462}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 484}, {\"ngram\": \"their strong grip\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The chalk helps absorb moisture on the hands and fingers, which eradicates the problem of sweaty palms and gymnasts losing their grip on the bar.\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The chalk\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 547}, {\"ngram\": \"moisture\", \"from\": 561, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"the hands\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 582}, {\"ngram\": \"fingers\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 613, \"to\": 624}, {\"ngram\": \"sweaty palms\", \"from\": 628, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 653}, {\"ngram\": \"their grip\", \"from\": 661, \"to\": 671}, {\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 675, \"to\": 682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It also helps decrease friction which allows gymnasts to have a smooth spin during rotations.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"friction\", \"from\": 708, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnasts\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 738}, {\"ngram\": \"a smooth spin\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"rotations\", \"from\": 768, \"to\": 777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Female gymnasts also apply chalk to their feet before a routine on the balance beam.\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Female gymnasts\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 795}, {\"ngram\": \"chalk\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 812}, {\"ngram\": \"their feet\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 826}, {\"ngram\": \"a routine\", \"from\": 834, \"to\": 843}, {\"ngram\": \"the balance beam\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Male gymnasts also apply chalk on their armpits for the parallel bars as they swing with their upper arms.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 972, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Male gymnasts\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 879}, {\"ngram\": \"chalk\", \"from\": 891, \"to\": 896}, {\"ngram\": \"their armpits\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 913}, {\"ngram\": \"the parallel bars\", \"from\": 918, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"their upper arms\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Without chalk, there would be a drastic rise in falls.\", \"from\": 974, \"to\": 1028, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"chalk\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 987}, {\"ngram\": \"a drastic rise\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"falls\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1027}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gymnastics chalk is made from Magnesium Carbonate (MgCO3).\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gymnastics chalk\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"Magnesium Carbonate\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1079}, {\"ngram\": \"MgCO3\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It can typically be purchased as a powder, in a block or in liquid form, although that is usually more expensive.\", \"from\": 1089, \"to\": 1202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a powder\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1130}, {\"ngram\": \"a block\", \"from\": 1135, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"liquid form\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is different to the chalk used in used in classrooms, which is made from Calcium Sulphate (CaSO4) and does not absorb moisture in the same way.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1350, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1298, \"end\": 1303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calcium_sulfate\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"CaSO4\", \"types\": [\"Q11173\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Calcium_sulfate\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/C